// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0473 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: e5aa5ef9-f378-5e87-aa21-81110bdf1c98

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.10*")
